25|$|Prayer: Both {{traditional}} Muslims and the Nation of Islam {{believe that}} the five daily prayers (salat) are mandatory. The leader of the NOI, Elijah Muhammad, was once quoted as saying to his followers <b>that</b> <b>prayer</b> is 'necessary for spiritual advancement'.|$|E
